theme.name: Crazy  Quilt
theme.author: CollieSmile
theme.description:
I made 8 Personas that I called WhirlAway Patterns, and each was in a different color. If you saw those & had trouble picking a one, these 3 may be for you. Crazy Quilt, Crazier Quilt and Craziest Quilt are all scrambled rainbow versions of my WhirlAways!  Each one is a bit wilder than the one before it.(red, scarlet, orange, golden yellow, green, blue, purple, dark violet, deep pink, zig zags, multicolored c0l1)

This is an original Abstract design by CollieSmile
